{"tid":866818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔怕再被block 侵侵粉絲交友軟件面世","createTime":"2018-10-18T07:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T07:33:38.000Z","uid":150685,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"80da2a8456fafb87940697569821d6ec164c5031","tid":866818,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.donalddaters.com/public/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.donalddaters.com%2Fpublic%2F&d=0m12r7NV4xNHaDqtC9LzjKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=63086f20\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.donalddaters.com/public/</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對許多使用交友App約會的網民來說，政治傾向是挑選對象的重要條件。香港有黃藍之分，美國也有分保守派、自由派。許多人在Tinder等交友軟體自我介紹，會直接打上「支持特朗普的，往左滑」、「你投特朗普的話，就不要來浪費我的時間」。讓許多「侵侵粉絲」感到不友善也很不方便。<br />\n<br />\n一款專為特朗普支持者設計的交友軟體「Donald Daters」，周一正式在蘋果和Android平台推出。目的就是為了讓廣大的特朗普支持者「抱團取暖」，至少在政治上觀點上能取得共鳴。其功能和其它主流交友軟體類似，當互相有好感時便能開起聊天視窗。<br />\n<br />\n根據2016年Tinder一項調查，71%的用戶會因政治傾向不同，與約會對象告吹。「Donald Daters」行政總裁Emily Moreno說：「許多年輕的特朗普支持者，被自由派弄得根本無法約會、見面......所以我們創造新平台，讓特朗普支持者不再害怕討論政治。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181017/58804300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F58804300&d=0m12r7NV4xNHaDqtC9LzjKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=b9a11bf6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F58804300&h=83ade90d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181017/58804300</a>"},{"pid":"6bdfe69f28c85b90255a51043a99ccfd5951d9ec","tid":866818,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:33:38.000Z","msg":"這個應用程式與你的裝置不相容。<br />\n<br />\n點解裝唔到架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}